CMorseRunner — CW Contest Pile-up Trainer (C++/Qt6)
====================================================

This project is a C++/Qt6 rewrite derived from MorseRunner by
Alex Shovkoplyas VE3NEA (https://www.dxatlas.com/MorseRunner/).
The DSP algorithms, state-machine logic, and numeric constants were
adapted from the original Delphi/Pascal source code.

